'''''ñguruk''''' (or ''(ñ)guruk'') is a [[Primitive Quendian]] word of unknown exact meaning. It was an elaborate word signifying an element of great terror to the [[Elves]].<ref name=AC>{{WJ|AC}}, pp. 389-390, 415 (Author's note 27)</ref>
==Etymology==

*[[Primitive Quendian]] ''(g)ruk'' (from [[Sundocarme|root]] [[RUKU]]) + [[Sundocarme|Root]] [[NGUR]]<ref name=AC/>

